####### Mirror the current site [hosted on GoDaddy]

- open Terminal

httrack

- At prompts:
	- Enter project name:
	rebeccal

	- Enter URLs (separated by commas or blank spaces) :
	http://www.rebeccal.com

	- Action
	4

# This will mirror the entire site (all pages, images, etc., not just index.html)
# Files will be saved to /Users/amanda/websites/

- Move files to Applications > MAMP > htdocs > rleder





###### Open MAMP application

- Applications > MAMP 

- Left sidebar: turn Appache on







######## Browser

- http://localhost:8888/rleder/

# if any of the link tags are pointing at index-2.html change them to index.html


